Package Creator

CLI Usage
---------

creator.py --help
    - Displays the available CLI parameters
    
creator.py --overwrite
    - Overwrites the package if one already exists
    
creator.py --folder FOLDER
    - Uses FOLDER as the working directory
    
creator.py init
    - Initializes a new package in the current working directory
      which may be moved using --folder
    
creator.py set PROPERTY VALUE
    - Sets the value of a property on a package. VALUE should always be wrapped
      in quotes.
      
    creator.py set depends "pkg1,version;pkg2,version"
        - Sets the dependencies of the current package to depend on both pkg1
          and pkg2
      
creator.py show PROPERTY
    - Displays the value of a property on a package.
    
creator.py clear PROPERTY
    - Clears the value of a property on a package.